title: The Best of the Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of the Dan Patrick Show
description:
Covino & Rich are filling in for Dan Patrick on your Thursday morning and have fun talking Baker Mayfield, with an actual fajita comparison. The fellas look at the Browns side of things.. could Jimmy G. be a stop-gap? Plus, Aaron Rodgers has ink and Covino has a man cave dream!
